import React, {useState, useEffect} from 'react'; import mobil from '../images/mobil.jpg' import axios from 'axios'; const Dashboard = () => { const [mobil, setMobil] = useState([]); useEffect(()=> { getMobil(); }, []); const getMobil = async () => { const response = await axios.get("http://localhost:5000/mobil"); setMobil(response.data); }; return ( <> {mobil.map((mobil, index)=> (

{mobil.nama}

{mobil.harga}

))} ) } export default Dashboard
